This cereal also provides a good source of seven essential vitamins and minerals to help you get a great start. Not just for breakfast, Kellogg's Disney's Frozen 2 Cereal is a tasty and nutritious addition to any meal or snack any time of the day. You can enjoy some cereal as a crunchy snack with friends after school, share some around the table while playing board games, or bring out a box of fun Frozen 2 cereal as a late-night treat at your next sleepover. Kellogg's Disney's Frozen 2 Cereal also makes a great addition to your favorite yogurt or as the base for a homemade trail mix the mouthwatering options are endless. A travel-ready food, Kellogg's Disney's Frozen 2 Cereal can be packed in baggies to accompany lunchboxes, after-school snacks, and busy, on-the-go moments. Just add your favorite milk or enjoy as a crispy treat straight from the box.
